touch note.txt
nano ~/.local/share/applications/note.desktop

[Desktop Entry]
Name=Quick Note
Comment=Open my note.txt quickly
Exec=mousepad /home/john/note.txt
Icon=accessories-text-editor
Terminal=false
Type=Application
Categories=Utility;

chmod +x ~/.local/share/applications/note.desktop

Lastly, ook for the desktop entry in the application menu and add it to the dock.
